{"tid":1639753,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"東周刊：民陣記者會幕後大台=泛民","createTime":"2019-10-08T17:02:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T17:20:26.000Z","uid":153,"like":5,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"b60ae32d21dd932649baf4c751bb7814223fb770","tid":1639753,"uid":153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T17:02:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pi8VWQk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fpi8VWQk.jpg&h=07f9f45f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n泛民打手全面進場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />清洗太平地"},{"pid":"7fd55aff78df271a1d0d025504265529d18ab547","tid":1639753,"uid":153,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T17:03:37.000Z","msg":"東周刊：民<span style=\"color: red;\">間</span>記者會幕後大台=泛民<br />\n<br />\n打錯字"},{"pid":"058194c6ca9a3f4060efd740498d72efeed4dd56","tid":1639753,"uid":262899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T17:04:32.000Z","msg":"幫你推～<br />\n<br />\n幫手推一推～ 感謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n被捕求助（對唔住手足）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1633560\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1633560</a>"},{"pid":"2c92db9c6664e46c69c78061a540858ec41d7d67","tid":1639753,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T17:05:28.000Z","msg":"（分析+行動）政府有意部署封網，封網後香港變新疆！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1639585\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1639585</a><br />\n<br />\n星期二（10月8日）早上，港鐵就宣布提前在晚上八點停駛，點解政府未卜先知出現動亂？其實政府有心製造一個長期嘅亂局，然後用緊急法立更多惡法，其中最近葉國謙就話要準備封網，呢樣嘢可以對香港抗爭造成極嚴重打擊。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><ins>斷網可毒啞香港人，新疆前車可鑑</ins></span></strong><br />\n斷網真係落實嘅話，<span style=\"color: red;\">最惡劣係好似新疆咁徹底斷網</span>，只有政府部門先可以上網，<span style=\"color: red;\">徹底封網的話，大家不但難以互通抗爭消息，而且香港訊息難以傳到海外，香港人也難以接收海外消息。西方人對香港嘅了解，只能經過政府嘅官方說法，或極少數流出嘅真相。</span><span style=\"color: gold;\">新疆早在2009年封網，同時限制境外人士到新疆旅遊，斷絕新疆對外聯繫，結果近年就出現新疆集中營。呢方面大家一定要警惕！</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>大家不能掉以輕心</strong><br />\n或者有人認為政府會顧及香港嘅國際環境唔會輕易斷網，但現在中共已經失去理性，當中央黔驢技窮，損害香港利益而徹底封網並非不可。就好似半年前大家都唸唔到香港已經失去遊行以及戴口罩嘅自由。<br />\n<br />\n本文為節錄，全文請到此瀏覽：<br />\n<br />\n（分析+行動）政府有意部署封網，封網後香港變新疆！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1639585\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1639585</a>"},{"pid":"a1f343df3e2c800c8f16fce851c4efb65614ba4d","tid":1639753,"uid":308486,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T17:06:25.000Z","msg":"被人發現咗添，死啦場運動會唔會就咁完㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02701c5075078ec239650328274f01be73b220dc","tid":1639753,"uid":323443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T17:07:27.000Z","msg":"大台已死，有事燒紙。"},{"pid":"edebb74c33a4f1bd5d191badd2b85c05ea0aa082","tid":1639753,"uid":53003,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T17:12:13.000Z","msg":"點算，黎智英又收錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6800177ca3fe66d42e42a2875fe003f45977f54f","tid":1639753,"uid":288707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T17:13:30.000Z","msg":"完了,隱藏左咁多個月出事了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54b01067625465534bfdbc9358579707e4ca1fbc","tid":1639753,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T17:13:47.000Z","msg":"我真係唔知呀 你好叻呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"589684a911f3ed9d09aa56e954947792f6b47bde","tid":1639753,"uid":100060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T17:15:02.000Z","msg":"嗌左小心d黃左啦依家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5d41727500eb00fa4ea2742b0fb84833e253548","tid":1639753,"uid":53415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime